/2025/03/buffy-reboot-characters-cast-hulu.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=1200%2C800 1200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/buffy-reboot-characters-cast-hulu.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=223%2C150 223w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/buffy-reboot-characters-cast-hulu.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=150%2C101 150w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/buffy-reboot-characters-cast-hulu.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=110%2C74 110w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" data-attachment-id=\"1235422703\" data-wp-size=\"nova_size__threebytwo_small_cropped\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1240\" height=\"840\" src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?w=650\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg 1240w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=200,135 200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=300,203 300w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=768,520 768w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=1024,694 1024w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=148,100 148w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=600,406 600w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=276,187 276w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=1000,677 1000w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=244,165 244w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=1160,786 1160w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=140,95 140w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=59,40 59w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=1200,813 1200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=248,168 248w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=497,337 497w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=996,675 996w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=295,200 295w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=590,400 590w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=1181,800 1181w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=221,150 221w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=443,300 443w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=886,600 886w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=150,102 150w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=110,75 110w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=285,193 285w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=320,217 320w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=640,434 640w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-linda-lavin-death-explained.jpg?resize=800,542 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e“We so wanted to honor her in the way that she deserved to be honored, so the question was, well, are we up to the task?” Kohan tells TVLine. “What do we have? Well, we have the truth. We have the person that we knew and we have the truth of her experience.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAdds Mutchnick, “Linda said to us at the very end that she wanted us to write everything that was going on for her into the show. She certainly didn’t think it was going to take the turn that it did, but it allowed us to think of it that way when sat down to write. Let’s actually write what happened to her and to us, and what it’s like to have such a jarring, horrifying experience and then have to still pick yourself up and move on. That’s what we tried to do with that episode.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eNow for another difficult question: What’s next? If you’ve seen any amount of \u003cem\u003eMid-Century Modern\u003c/em\u003e, you know how important Lavin is to the DNA of the show. Heck, it would be like if Estelle Getty’s character suddenly disappeared from \u003cem\u003eThe Golden Girls\u003c/em\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1240\" height=\"840\" src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?w=650\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg 1240w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=200,135 200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=300,203 300w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=768,520 768w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=1024,694 1024w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=148,100 148w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=600,406 600w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=276,187 276w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=1000,677 1000w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=244,165 244w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=1160,786 1160w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=140,95 140w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=59,40 59w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=1200,813 1200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=248,168 248w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=497,337 497w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=996,675 996w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=295,200 295w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=590,400 590w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=1181,800 1181w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=221,150 221w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=443,300 443w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=886,600 886w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=150,102 150w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=110,75 110w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=285,193 285w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=320,217 320w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=640,434 640w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mid-century-modern-pamela-adlon.jpg?resize=800,542 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eEnter \u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/t/pamela-adlon/\" id=\"auto-tag_pamela-adlon_1\" data-tag=\"pamela-adlon\"\u003ePamela Adlon\u003c/a\u003e as Bunny’s sister Mindy, who inherited more of her mother’s qualities than she cares to admit. Mindy recurs throughout the first season, and even though she turns down the boys’ offer to move into Sybil’s now-vacant room in the season finale, she’ll remain in their orbit.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e“Fingers crossed, we’ve already set it up,” Mutchnick says of Sybil’s replacement. “It was a happy accident that Mindy was written into the show. Pamela Adlon is a friend and a brilliant actress and just a great sound for this show. We’re hoping that, in the event we’re lucky enough to come back, that she will come back with us.”\n\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you’ve been bingeing \u003cem\u003eMid-Century Modern\u003c/em\u003e, let’s hear your thoughts: Are you enjoying your time with the Desert Queens? How do you think the show handled Lavin’s death? And what are you hoping to see in a potential second season? \u003cstrong\u003eGrade the Hulu comedy in our poll below, then drop a comment with your full review. \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
